#: user_guide/en.html:1335
msgid ""
"<span class= \"label_red\">WARNING</span> Be careful if you decide to use "
"the SSH feature without a password, because this allows open access to your "
"device. But if you are using a local wifi and turn on your device wifi for a "
"short time, this risk is negligible."
