#. type: Content of: <html><body><div><div>
#: user_guide/en.html:1553
msgid ""
"<span class=\"label_blue\">INFO</span> If you have a PocketBook device and "
"frontlight or warmth slider is not working in KOReader, please be sure that "
"in the PocketBook reader (which comes with your device) "
"<b>SmartLight-Auto</b> option is set to <b>Disabled</b>."
