"files. Two of the most known PDF libraries are <b>MuPDF</b> and "
"<b>Poppler</b> libraries. KOReader uses the <b>MuPDF</b> library, so the "
"highlights written to PDFs in KOReader are not currently visible on PDF "
"readers which uses the <b>Poppler</b> library. You can find a compatibility "
"list below. ‚úÖ means you can see your KOReader highlights in this "
"application, ‚ùå means you can't see them. And ‚ö†Ô∏è means the application needs "
"some plugin to show them. List is ordered alphabetically within categories."
