#. type: Content of: <html><body><div><table><tr><td><p>
#: user_guide/en.html:5801
msgid ""
"Run this profile when you enter this folder in file browser. You can use "
"this trigger to change the display mode of <span class= \"ui\">file "
"browser</span>. For example when you enter a certain folder you can change "
"the display mode from <b>mosaic</b> to <b>detailed</b> view."
